Package: smi
Title: Supervised Macroeconomic Index for IFRS9 Forward-Looking Modeling
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
 c(person(given = "Andrija",
             family = "Djurovic",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "djandrija@gmail.com")
      )
Maintainer: Andrija Djurovic <djandrija@gmail.com>
Description: The package offers functionalities for constructing the Supervised Macroeconomic Index, which can be used in IFRS9 forward-looking modeling to address some of the most challenging issues practitioners encounter during this process. These challenges primarily arise from the limited number of available observations.
